Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:11.72,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:12.86,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:38.21,Punchline-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch Line
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:02.39,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.19,0:02:06.68,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Campanella Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:14.90,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Miyazawa Kenji has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.24,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You! How...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:20.70,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to be clairvoyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.45,Punchline-Bullets,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Nor losing\Nto bullets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:24.91,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You should have known...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.71,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I still have bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:31.30,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,The hero of justice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.40,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,Strange Juice, is on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:39.05,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,So, now what? It's two against one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.27,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:45.51,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to show you my true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:49.85,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:51.23,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.76,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:58.56,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I can Yubafy, just like you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:02.29,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Except I have an expression \Nrate of 2,000 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:05.87,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what that means, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.54,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.17,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.72,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,What is your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:29.98,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say it's the \Ncreation of an ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.55,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,To destroy inferior humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to rule the world with only the superior W.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.47,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,W?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:39.45,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.24,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.74,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.21,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.74,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.13,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.06,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.96,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:57.20,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have your way any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.66,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Why say that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.41,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this to carry out your wishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.71,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:04.84,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.26,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.10,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.45,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.35,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to you, Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:15.85,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.11,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Just use this, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:19.38,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Cinnamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:23.61,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, my power! My power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.20,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.33,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:41.83,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.81,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.90,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,How is it that even you can Yubafy—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.10,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:00.11,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask to become this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.20,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.42,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.33,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.00,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.25,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika! Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.51,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.84,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:38.71,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What are you crying about, Rabura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:42.59,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.29,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Muhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:53.83,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's have a look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.41,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.42,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, Ito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.15,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoda Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.90,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,My homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:08.30,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a teacher do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:13.75,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I loved you, Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.86,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:21.34,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I loved you that I edited the video
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sent out the emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.19,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Then the person who killed Meiko and Moena...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:33.20,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I was possessed by the spirit of the \NQmay Group leader, Tsubouchi Qmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.89,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:38.08,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.65,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I made a contract with Tsubouchi's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.88,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for lending him \Nmy body, I would get my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.71,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.34,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.50,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ito was being harassed at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.81,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.48,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I was destined to be with Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.56,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,The people in our class got in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.94,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.00,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.79,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:15.58,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,In order to respond to your love, \NI have to punish them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.58,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a true test of love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.79,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.41,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,This guy gives me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:29.01,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Say, so that Tsubouchi's spirit is still inside you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:34.51,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,My body's useless to him as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.66,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the Yubafication.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:37.75,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.89,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,More accurately, it's Yubamenschification.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:44.24,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,When you're infected with the \Nso-called Hercules virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you undergo epigenetic effects \Nthat toggle genetic switches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.06,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It changes your body's composition,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you become able to exert \Npower beyond your limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.76,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that all the time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.18,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, there are limiters on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.92,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,When those limiters come off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.37,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You Yubafy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:06.38,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.61,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,But Yubafying comes with huge risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.53,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Doing it over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,causes severe damage and atrophy to the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.43,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.07,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.53,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened to Tsubouchi, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:25.99,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,And that cub was created in order \Nto allow his body to regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.44,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,With his extraordinary regenerative capacity,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he could evade death and Yubafy regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.28,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You disgust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.56,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,You're still so dishonest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:47.40,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have one last wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.88,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Ito, don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.02,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,Survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:55.63,Default,Kameotoko,0000,0000,0000,,That's my—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.01,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.01,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Ito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.36,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.39,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you say all that selfish crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.58,Default,StrangeJuice,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.81,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Possessed by a spirit, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.52,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.02,Punchline-Timeline,,0000,0000,0000,,The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.29,Punchline-New_Years_Banner,Text,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Year's Eve! Meikaemon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.79,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,And... why are we having nagashi soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.10,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Year's Eve. Soba is a mainstay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.38,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I get the soba part, but why nagashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:33.49,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally off-season.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.10,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it, Ito?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.51,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:39.96,Punchline-New_Years_Banner,,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Year's Eve! Meikaemon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.59,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so gloomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.11,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.13,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:48.05,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.62,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.86,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,At AFSPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.09,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I hacked into \Nthe U.S. military servers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but everything was normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.79,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:01.42,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if an asteroid were \Nreally going to hit us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the whole world would be \Nfreaking out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:08.17,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Year's Eve. \NLet's go back to Meikaemon's party
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and raise the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.00,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:15.63,Punchline-Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Year's Eve,\NMeikaemon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:23.65,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Sushi rice, sushi rice, chirashi sushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:29.99,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.42,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.15,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Not your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:41.90,Punchline-New_Years_Banner2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}It's New Year's Eve! Meikaemon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:39.09,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,But it's for our upcoming musical!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.91,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It's just lacking in girlish sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:45.21,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been in love \Nor anything, Mikatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.73,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,In love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.60,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I haven't met anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.92,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.42,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,There's one person, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:58.48,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, there's Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.84,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try falling in love with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.13,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.85,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,She already has!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.27,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.23,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,He's a girl, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:18.49,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.52,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Biologically, he's unmistakably female.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.49,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I kept it a secret until now \Nbecause it's a delicate issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:30.37,Punchline-Iridatsu_Yu,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Iridatsu Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.22,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,His true, registered legal name is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.34,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Iridatsu Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:34.63,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuta" is just a name he gave himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:42.71,Punchline-New_Years_Banner2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Year's Eve! Meikaemon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:37.74,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,S-Speaking of, where {\i1}is{\i0} Yuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.41,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I invited him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.72,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.98,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you have any more \Nsecrets or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:48.63,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,About Iridatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.12,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,That works, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.80,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about your and Mikatan's past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.42,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.99,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:08.87,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,It was eight years ago, in the summer, \Nthat I met Narugino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:12.63,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,It was a stormy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.35,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:21.12,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.49,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Daihatsu Meika.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:29.50,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a robot that's come to shelter, \Nraise, and support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:34.52,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the apartment burn down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:41.03,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Narugino escaped from a facility with \Nthe help of someone named Ishigata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:45.03,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,But they were found right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:51.00,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,And Ishigata took the \Npursuers down with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:57.79,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to take Narugino away from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.42,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,We went further and further \Nnorth, and ended up deep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the mountains of Aomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:09.26,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,We rented a shabby old shack \Nand started to live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.76,Punchline-Subtitles,Text,0000,0000,0000,,It's over. I'm superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.64,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I trained her, day in and day out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to bring out the strength that \Nshe possessed within herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:27.24,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,It was when she was 13 years old and \Nout shopping that my efforts bore fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:30.02,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.24,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:40.29,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, she's been \Nkicking ass all over the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:43.25,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,catching bad guys one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:49.60,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Tsugaru saw \NNarugino, and called her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:51.01,Punchline-Newspaper_Horizontal,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero of Tsugaru \N{\fs24}Pantyhose Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.97,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,"Pantyhose Girl"?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.82,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help that. It's to protect your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:14:00.16,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want to become a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.59,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to become an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.59,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.60,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,You have to become a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.73,Punchline-Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,or we can't form the secret \NJustice Punch squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:12.35,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,That name's so lame. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.47,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to call it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.42,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Like, Pretty Cutie Moon—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.88,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Too long! And you're ripping\Noff a bunch of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:25.90,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you were born to become a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.88,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,That's your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:30.14,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.64,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.52,Punchline-Flashback,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.90,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Your new costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:46.47,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, you're Strange Juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.95,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to fight evil as a new hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.51,Punchline-Flashback,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,in Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.79,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you came to Koraikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:01.54,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,We're thinking of calling off \Nthe hero thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.25,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.07,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.46,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Narugino is a Yubafier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:09.01,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Is her body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:12.67,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.46,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,After we were together this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.89,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta-kun wasn't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.90,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's out somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.03,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.45,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.07,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:04.56,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Meika, we're out of fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.99,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.19,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bottle rocket that\NI've kept for a special occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.51,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,A special occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.96,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I never saw one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.72,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.12,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.00,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just remembered I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.00,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:22.94,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.75,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, come by soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.38,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:38.06,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to refill my medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.25,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Narugino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:42.64,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I have to let everyone know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:49.79,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Miyazawa Kenji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.12,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:02.28,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I call it the Kaku-maker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:03.16,Punchline-Kaku-Maker,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kaku-maker
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:06.02,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, where's the bottle rocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.18,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.06,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,See it up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:14.15,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter today, Miyako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.80,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,B,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.62,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,C,0000,0000,0000,,We interrupt this program \Nto deliver breaking news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.77,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,C,0000,0000,0000,,Asteroid VR-1, which until \Nnow was not expected to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:25.31,Punchline-News,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Two kilometer diameter asteroid strike imminent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:25.31,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,collide with Earth, will imminently...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.35,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Will imminently collide with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:33.57,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, Asteroid VR-1's collision is imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.57,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:40.05,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeijini nyopurasara,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:46.13,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put a spell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:51.82,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeijini nyopurakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.54,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:53.96,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,That song...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.46,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.76,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Mikatan, what's keeping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.93,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.62,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.88,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:03.57,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.73,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:10.75,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry up, or I'll launch the firework!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.73,Default,Mikatan,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to listen to you more later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.18,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,A promise for later, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.86,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.24,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Come down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.17,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What's your deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.29,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.64,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:38.38,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Meika said everything was \Nnormal on the AFSPC servers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:43.22,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And the Qmay Group was trying to \Nmake W, but it's not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.26,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know the answer once \Nyou have your body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:50.45,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I need some book called \Nthe Nandala Gandala for tha—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.56,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.98,Punchline-Nandala_Gandala,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Indian Holy Text\NNandala Gandala
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you messing with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.20,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,You could have made a better fake than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.24,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Just look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.45,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.96,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's all blank, with just one word!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.75,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is a U-turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.50,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Just as it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.67,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No, what does it {\i1}mean{\i0}—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.16,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to go back in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.64,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,If I were, when would you go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.60,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,To before everything began...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.65,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,December 21st.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:35.84,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,That alone isn't enough \Nto take you back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:37.65,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,There's one other thing you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:42.78,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,A strong desire to save someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:46.64,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to tell you the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.13,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, this history is a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.38,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a future that mustn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.69,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Change this history.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:02.41,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I failed in my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:08.22,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Many of me have attempted it \Nand made the same mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:14.77,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I leave my hopes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:18.41,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\i1}all{\i0} of our hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.78,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.03,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta, wish for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.53,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Wish hard, from the bottom of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:29.29,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,That desire will grant you power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:35.42,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to change destiny. History, Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.44,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.03,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change history.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:00.44,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,For Meika. For Rabura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.98,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,For Ito.
